Title: Why Heaven Gets High Marks
---
That simple happiness that comes from sometimes seeing someone you want to
 see --
what is the source of that feeling? Oh, you know. I talk about it so much.
Why heaven gets such high marks is because whenever you bump into
anyone there, you always become delighted.
